### ============================================================
### SCHOOL SYSTEM - REST CLIENT EXAMPLES FOR GET /:id
### ============================================================
### 
### Este arquivo contém exemplos REST Client para testar
### todos os endpoints GET /:id implementados
###
### Como usar: Abra com a extensão REST Client do VS Code
### Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada requisição
###

@host = http://localhost:3000
@validId = 1
@invalidId = 99999

### ============================================================
### ALUNOS - Get by ID
### ============================================================

### GET Aluno (sucesso - 200 OK)
GET {{host}}/alunos/{{validId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### GET Aluno (erro - 404 Not Found)
GET {{host}}/alunos/{{invalidId}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### GET Alunos (todos - 200 OK)
GET {{host}}/alunos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Criar Aluno (para testes)
POST {{host}}/alunos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "matricula": "2025001",
  "dataNascimento": "2010-05-15",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "telefone": "44999990000",
  "turma": "7A"
}

